The Jamaican High Commision in Abuja, Nigeria Welcomes all Jamaicans in Nigeria, Cameroon, Ghana, Senegal and Sierre Leone.

The Jamaican High Comission in Abuja the capital of the Federal Republic of Nigeria provides information and assistance to Jamaican Nationals in the West African States under its jurisdiction. These countries include the Federal Republic of Nigeria, Republics of Cameroon, Ghana, Senegal and Sierre Leone.
